    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Puzzle Milk Tea is a match 3 arcade game where players can pop boba on their field in different game modes. Starting up a match is as easy as picking a mode, picking a drink, picking a level, and playing!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Launch boba into similar colors to pop them</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/2598afa15654585fb7dc8ad2f0b190e3.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/2598afa15654585fb7dc8ad2f0b190e3.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/2598afa15654585fb7dc8ad2f0b190e3.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dropping boba causes chains</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/5747e316df9258e0a8b7bf37393e073d.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/5747e316df9258e0a8b7bf37393e073d.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/5747e316df9258e0a8b7bf37393e073d.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pick from 4 different modes or play the tutorial to learn the game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/aaa9da094337aaff583c5d95613365d3.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/aaa9da094337aaff583c5d95613365d3.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/aaa9da094337aaff583c5d95613365d3.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Race - Pop all boba as quickly as you can</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Survival - Pop boba while the board is continuously filled</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Battle - Pop boba to send boba to other players</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless - Pop boba with no limits</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Tutorial - Learn how to play</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Customize your drink and boba</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/afa965bd5a237480db62e9640e7a95c9.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/afa965bd5a237480db62e9640e7a95c9.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/afa965bd5a237480db62e9640e7a95c9.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Pick from many levels to play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/34c3bf015846a406f7361ab6b18507a0.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/34c3bf015846a406f7361ab6b18507a0.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/34c3bf015846a406f7361ab6b18507a0.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with friends locally and battle against CPUs</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/e9d8250aa5748b9d8514b3ebe6219d4b.poster.avif?t=1770666858\" width=854 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/e9d8250aa5748b9d8514b3ebe6219d4b.webm?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3197490/extras/e9d8250aa5748b9d8514b3ebe6219d4b.mp4?t=1770666858\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Capsule Art by: Ronnie Nguyen</p>",
